## 🛠️ Tools & Technologies
- **Python:** Pandas, NumPy, Scikit-learn, Matplotlib, Seaborn
- **Machine Learning:** Logistic Regression, SMOTE
- **Statistics:** Odds Ratios, 95% Confidence Intervals

## 📈 Model Performance
| Metric | Value |
|--------|-------|
| AUC Score | 0.664 |
| High Risk Recall | 62% |
| Precision (High Risk) | 25% |

